2007-09-26 Wednesday 05:30  Rocky Bernstein

	* lib/iso9660/iso9660_fs.c: iso9660_open_ext_private(): close image
	  filecupon error.

	  Leds to an open file descriptor making it impossible of e.g.
	  unmounting a CDROM containing the file. Savannah bug #21147.

