2006-12-20 Wednesday 09:26  Rocky Bernstein

	* lib/iso9660/iso9660_fs.c: Symlinks were sharing stat_buf so
	  freeing one made the pointer to the other invalid. Allocate a
	  separate entry for each symlink.

	  Bug report and patch provided by Antti Perälä. Savannah bug
	  #18563

