	  >= 0.

2006-02-27 Monday 10:10  Diego 'Flameeyes' Pettenò

	* include/cdio/Makefile.am: Remove cdio_include.h at distclean
	  rather than in clean, as it's done for config.h. Doesn't require
	  to re-run ./configure at make clean.

2006-02-27 Monday 09:48  Diego 'Flameeyes' Pettenò

	* lib/driver/portable.h: Use preprocessor's #error instead of
	  adding invalid code, makes the error more verbose and waste less
	  time (as it stops during preprocessing instead of compiling).

