2005-04-30 Saturday 07:15  Rocky Bernstein

	* include/cdio/cdda.h, lib/cdda_interface/interface.c,
	  lib/cdda_interface/scan_devices.c: Simplify endian determination
	  - thanks to suggestions of Steve Schultz

