2005-02-22 Tuesday 09:55  Rocky Bernstein

	* lib/iso9660/iso9660.c, test/isofs-m1.right, test/monvoisin.right:
	  iso9660_get_dtime hack: we've seen it happen that everything
	  except gmtoff is zero and the expected date is the beginning of
	  the epoch. So we accept 6 numbers being zero. I'm also not sure
	  if using the of the Epoch is also the right thing to do either.

