2004-07-10 Saturday 11:06  Rocky Bernstein

	* lib/: image.h, image_common.h: Hoist some more common image
	  routines and make image drivers look more common. In particular
	  we now have a "cue", "source", and "access-mode" parameters
	  defined even when "cue" and "source" are the same as in NRG.

	  The _img_private_t's for the image drivers are now more similar
	  if not the same.

	  Some memory leaks when there are error conditions in opening
	  image drivers have been fixed.

