	* doc/libcdio.texi: libcdio.info was missing a @dircategory and
	  @direntry section.

	  See
	  http://savannah.nongnu.org/bugs/?func=detailbug&bug_id=6470&group_id=3845

	  Thanks to dweimer for pointing this out and providing a patch.

